data.description: **LOVELY WESTSIDE HOME** Welcome to this beautiful home on the Westside, showcasing some of California's best landscaping with eye-catching palm trees and an easy-to-maintain front yard for standout curb appeal. Inside, you'll find a warm family room with a cozy fireplace and stylish upgraded flooring that extends throughout the home. The heart of the house is a stunning chef's kitchen equipped with modern appliances, Corian countertops, a dining area, and direct access to the backyard patio -- perfect for both cooking and socializing. This home also features three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, including a master suite with backyard access and an en-suite bathroom with upgraded counters and a luxurious walk-in shower. The backyard offers plenty of space to create your dream outdoor area, ideal for entertaining or simply enjoying the outdoors. Located in a sought-after area, this home is expected to attract attention quickly. Interested in making this house your home? Contact us now for a personal tour.
